\id 3JN - Zanaki 3 John
\h 3 Yohana
\toc3 3 Yohana
\toc2 3 Yohana
\toc1 Enyaarubha ya katatu ya Yohana
\mt2 Enyaarubha ya katatu ya
\mt1 Yohana
\imt1 Obhutaangiro
\ip Munyaarubha ya katatu, Yohana aramukaamira omuutu wuno yaari arabhirikirwa Gaayo. Gaayo yaari mugumiru bhukongʼu kwo okumwiikirirya Krisito. Yaari arabhasakirya abheegya abhaandi bhano bhaari bhariiruguura mukyaaro kya Asia, kwiiguru yo kuraarika Amangʼana Amazomu go obhuheene. Yohana aramukaamira okumutoongera ageenderere okubhasakirya abheegya bhayo.
\ip Munyaarubha yino, Yohana aragaamba omuutu wuno yaari arabhirikirwa Diotirefe. Omuutu wuyo, yaari arasakya kuribhira abhaatu bhe ekanisa bhataginihya abheegya bhano bhaari bhareegya Amangʼana Amazomu. Bhuundi ne ewe, Yohana aragaamba muutu omuzomu wuno ariikara kwo obhuheene, eriina ryaaye Demetirio.
\c 1
\s1 Obhukeerya
\p 
\v 1 Enye omukaruka we ekanisa, nirakukaamira awe Gaayo omuseegwa waane. Nikuseegiri kwe eheene.
\p 
\v 2 Bhoono, omuseegwa waane, ndakusabhira ku Taatabhugya obhe muhoru, na amangʼana gaazo goosi gageenderere kisi kyeego okugeenderera mumangʼana ga mukoro.
\v 3 Nikazomererwa bhukongʼu, hano abharikyeetu abharebhe hano bhiiziri eno no okunibhuurira kubha, awe orageenderera okugwaata obhuheene no okwiikara kwo obhuheene.
\v 4 Kitariho kigiro kino kikuuniha obhuzomererwa bhukongʼu kukira okwiigwa kubha, abhaana bhaane bharageenderera okwiikara kwo obhuheene.
\s1 Obhuheene bhwa Gaayo
\p 
\v 5 Omuseegwa waane, awe ni mwiikirirya kugano okubhakorera abhahiiri bheetu, yiingabha ni bhagini bhaazo.
\v 6 Abhahiiri bhayo bhabhabhuuriiri abhaatu bhe ekanisa ya hano kwiiguru yo obhuseegi bhwaazo. Nirakwiisasaama, ogeenderere okubhasakirya kyeego ekumuzomera Taatabhugya, okubha bhageenderere no orugeendo rwaabhu.
\v 7 Hano bhaari kugeenderera murugeendo rwaabhu okumuhokeerya Yeesu Krisito, bhatasuungʼaaniri obhusakirya bhwobhwoosi okurwa kubhaatu bhano bhatamumenyiri Taatabhugya.
\v 8 Kweego, etwe tureenderwa kubhasakirya abhaatu kya bhayo, okubha tubhe twiisaangiinie hamwe nabho mumirimo gyo okuraarika obhuheene.
\s1 Diotirefe na Demetirio
\p 
\v 9 Nikayikaamira ekanisa enyaarubha nguhi, nawe Diotirefe ewe araseega okwiituura embere kyeego niwe omukaangati wa bhoosi, atakwiikirirya obhunagya bhweetu.
\v 10 Kweego, niraaze eyo, niragatuura kubhweero amangʼana gano akukora na kyeego akuruusya obhuzeema iguru weetu kumangʼana amabhi. Gatari gayo ego, nawe araanga okuginihya abhahiiri bheetu bhano bhari murugeendo. Na abhaatu bhano bhakweenda kubhaginihya, ewe arabharekya no okubhaheebha bharwe mukanisa.
\p 
\v 11 Bhoono, omuseegwa waane Gaayo, oteega amangʼana amabhiihu, nawe weege amangʼana amazomu. Wowoosi wuno akukora amazomu, wuyo ni mwaana wa Taatabhugya. Nawe wuno akukora amabhiihu, wuyo atamumenyiri Taatabhugya.
\p 
\v 12 Abhaatu bhoosi bharabhuga kubha, Demetirio ni muutu muzomu, no obhwiikari bhwaaye bhurariingʼaana no obhuheene. Naabhe na neetwe, turabhuga ego, no omenyiri kubha obhumenyeekererya bhweetu ni bhwe eheene.
\s1 Amangʼana go okuraga
\p 
\v 13 Nina amangʼana maaru go okukaama, nawe nitakweenda kukaama gayo kunyaarubha.
\v 14 Ndiisiga kukutaarira no okukeerenia hamwe naawe obhusyo kwo obhusyo.
\p 
\v 15 Omureembe gubhe hamwe naawe. Abhasaani bhaazo bha hano bharakukeerya. Na naawe, obhakeerye abhasaani bheetu bhe eyo, kumariina gaabhu.
